===================================================================A comprehensive .gitignore file.Save this in the root directory of your project as ".gitignore"===================================================================--- Project-Specific Ignores ---Folder you wanted to ignore:Mathworks/--- Dependencies ---These folders are installed by package managers and can be huge./node_modules/bower_components/vendor/venv/packages/Pods--- Build & Output ---These are files generated by your compiler or build process./build/dist/bin/obj/out*.o*.exe*.dll*.so--- Logs ---Log files are specific to your machine and shouldn't be in Git..lognpm-debug.logyarn-debug.log*yarn-error.log*--- Large Media Files ---Git is not designed to store large binary files.*.mp4*.mov*.avi*.zip*.tar.gz*.iso*.psd--- OS & System Files ---Files created by your operating system..DS_Store.DS_Store?._*.Spotlight-V100.Trashesehthumbs.dbThumbs.db--- IDE & Editor Settings ---These are your personal editor settings..vscode/.idea/*.swp*.swo*.sublime-workspace*.sublime-project.nvmrc--- Sensitive Information ---Never commit environment variables or secret keys..env.env.*!.env.example